      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、猫！？　さっきまで猫なんていなかったのに\n一体どこから現れたんだ！？",
      "startTime": 6.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、あの子は……\n閉鎖空間に入る前に見かけた三毛猫じゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 11.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……\n見ろ、あの三毛猫、口に何かを咥えているぞ！",
      "startTime": 17.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "折りたたんだ紙……みたいですね\nなんの紙でしょう？",
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三毛猫",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "にゃーん",
      "startTime": 26.5333335876,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 26.3000002543
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5199.999745699998,
          "startTime": 31.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　これ、私に……？\n何か書いてありますね。これは……曲名？",
      "startTime": 32.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……これ、ハルヒ達と一緒に考えた\nライブのセットリストです！",
      "startTime": 42.8666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "お祭りの時に、みんなで何を歌うか話し合って\n私が紙に書き留めたんです",
      "startTime": 48.9333374023,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2633.329264400004,
          "startTime": 51.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "見て下さい、ここにステージで歌うメンバーの\n名前が書いてあります",
      "startTime": 54.2666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "涼宮ハルヒ、朝比奈みくる、長門有希……\nそれに怜、千紗、芽衣、沙季の名前も……",
      "startTime": 61.0666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "間違いありません\nこの紙は、お祭りの時にハルヒと一緒に書いた物です",
      "startTime": 68.000004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、あれは夢じゃなかったんだ……",
      "startTime": 73.0831820167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "お祭りのステージは……\nハルヒと私が一緒に歌ったのは現実だったんですね",
      "startTime": 81.8666692097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三毛猫",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "にゃーん",
      "startTime": 86.6137522376,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 86.4137522376
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あの三毛猫……\nまるで怜に、こっちに来いと誘っているようだな",
      "startTime": 90.5000147501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "ひょっとして、そっちに行けばハルヒに会えるの？\nなぜだか分からないけど、そう感じる……",
      "startTime": 100.6666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "この先にハルヒが……SOS団のみんながいる……\n私が一歩踏み出せば、またあの場所に行ける……",
      "startTime": 111.9000096637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "怜……その先に行ったら、戻れない気がする\n二度と会えなくなる気が……それでも、行くのか？",
      "startTime": 122.2000096637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……私は……",
      "startTime": 127.9738671299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "三毛猫ちゃん……ごめんなさい\nやっぱり私、そっちには行けないわ",
      "startTime": 139.0666803994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "ここには大事な人達がいるの\n大切な仲間がいるの",
      "startTime": 145.4000198362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "みんなとやりたいことがまだまだ沢山あるから……\n私は行けないわ",
      "startTime": 151.9666844683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "だからハルヒに、「元気でね」って\n伝えておいてくれる？",
      "startTime": 157.1000086464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "それと、「あんまりみくると有希を\n困らせるんじゃないわよ」って",
      "startTime": 162.1333318071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三毛猫",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
