      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_03-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "私達……戻って来れたんですよね？\nさっきまでのは夢……じゃないですよね？",
      "startTime": 188.999991353,
